name: First Light | Last Light
description:
The state of my life: week 255. 
On my birthday I want to share this work with you. It reflects my uncertainties, the state of my body and spirit, scars, and fingerprints of the people I met. And of course a little particle of light...

For the past 3 years, I was perfecting this work with the elements I took from real life, and now it's ready to be converted into the blockchain.

And I continue to merge with MetaVerse.

3250x4600
Soft: Cinema 4d, Redshift Render, AE, real fingerprints, and other tips.
